::Magmatron::

    "Yes of course, I will allow you to have acess to all my repair tools, 
but be warned you will be under watch." Magmatron said. He then showed 
Phobias to the area for matenance and then went to his quarters. He decided 
to take a nap. On his bed he couldn't help but hink of what had happened 
since he had arrived. He was starting to get tired of the Beast Wars, but he 
had a mission, he couldn't let anything stop him.
